Extension Zoom Workplace.




























































Enhance your Zoom experience with the Zoom Workplace Chrome Extension. This extension allows you to easily adjust the brightness and background color of the Zoom website to suit your preferences. With a simple slider and color picker, you can customize the look and feel of the page for a more comfortable viewing experience. Perfect for users who want more control over their Zoom interface.
